JOHANNESBURG - American school guidance counsellor Veronica Nash-Poleate rose to social media stardom when she posted her video clip 'Don t Go in the Shark s House' on youtube it garnered 20 million views.Known as Sister Pooh, Nash-Poleate has degrees in psychology and education, she would address viewers as her 'congregation' and posted several clips advising congregants on everyday life issues.Soon after her stardom she signed a deal with TV channel TLC in which she would do house calls giving people advice.Click on the above video to see Sister Pooh advise congregants to go to the beach but not the ocean which she describes as the shark's house. eNCA